UID:10434588-1774555200-1774756800@golatindance.com
SUMMARY:16th Annual San Francisco Salsa Festival - 10% Discount
DESCRIPTION:Use promo code GOLD to save 10% on your pass!\nCelebrating our 16th year!! \nA weekend of world-class of Live Bands every night\, DJ’s\, performances\, social dancing\, competition and workshops with top salsa instructors. \nDear Bay Area dance community and our friends from around the world\, we’re excited to announce our 16th Annual SF Festival coming up in March 26-28\, 2026. \nOver the past 25 years we have traveled the globe\, everywhere from Mexico to China\, Korea\, Japan\, Canada\, England\, and Italy. We’ve had the opportunity to live abroad\, teach workshops and shows\, and experience an incredible life in the world salsa community.\nAlong the way\, we have been to the most amazing salsa congresses and festivals. We’ve made many friends and met the most amazing dancers in the world. The social dancing\, workshops\, and shows have brought so much fun and joy to people. Nothing could have been possible without this beautiful dance we call salsa. Its presence attracts people and ties them firmly. \nSpecial Guest Live Bands each night !!! \nSCHEDULE: \nTHURSDAY NIGHT / Welcome Party March 26\, 2026 \nAt El Valenciano\n1553 Valencia St\, San Francisco\, CA \n8:00pm – Doors Open\n9:15pm – Salsa Lesson with John and Liz\n11pm – Dance showcase\n10pm – 1:30am – Social dance all night\nTheme TBA💥🎉 \nLive band : TBA\n$25 Pre-Sale til 3/24\n$35 at the Door\nVenmo at @JohnandLizproductions \nBOOK Hotel only $159 a night til 2/15 (will get SOLD OUT) \nFRIDAY NIGHT / March 27\, 2026 \nSF Airport Marriott Waterfront\n1800 Old Bayshore Hwy.\nBurlingame\, CA \n12- 4pm WORKSHOPS \n4:00pm Tech Rehearsal for all performers \n5:00pm\n-2am Doors Open\n6pm Competition(call time 5:30pm)\n8:00pm Performance Showcase (Call time 7:30pm)\n9:30 pm Social dancing to live band and Guest Dj’s\nEnjoy your Salsa room with DJ SUPER CHINO and Bachata room with Guest DJ’s \nLive Band: TBA \nSATURDAY NIGHT / March 28\, 2026 \nSF Airport Marriott Waterfront\n1800 Old Bayshore Hwy.\nBurlingame\, CA \n4:00pm Tech Rehearsal for all performers \n9am – 4pm Beginner\, Intermediate and Master Bootcamps \n4-8:30pm Breaking news: The 3rd SF Salsa Vinyl Expo and social dancing by guest DJ’s \nDoors Open 7:00pm – 2am\n8:30pm Performance Showcase (Call time 8pm)\n9:30 pm Social dancing to live band and DJ SUPER CHINO\nEnjoy your Salsa room with DJ SUPER CHINO and guest Dj’s Bachata Room \nLive Band: LIVE GUEST TBA!!!\nVIP Table available (contact liz at 510-697-1892) \nGroup or Student Discounts – Discount ticket pricing is available for large groups or for Students. For more information\, contact us at liz@johnandlizproductions.com. \nFor more details\, schedule\, a list of performers\, and competition information\, visit http://sfsalsafestival.com. http://www.sfsalsafestival.com/\nor 510-697-1892 \nWe want to thank all of our coordinators and volunteers for their hard work\, and all of you for supporting our event. Let’s enjoy this weekend as much as we can and continue to support our amazing salsa community here in the Bay “Life” target=”_blank” title=”Area.\n“Life”>Area.\n“Life\, my friends\, is the art of getting together.” Therefore\, it is our honor and pleasure to organize another great salsa event here in the San Francisco Bay Area. \nLovingly\,\nJohn Narvaez & Elizabeth Rojas\nwww.johnandlizproductions.com \n 
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/16th-annual-san-francisco-salsa-festival-march-26-28-2026/
LOCATION:San Francisco Airport Marriott Waterfront\, 1800 Old Bayshore Highway\, Burlingame\, CA\, 94010\, United States
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/297537_image_604508361_1411290084341529_8058720536431562521_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
