SUMMARY:Pexava Monthly Matinee Socials
DESCRIPTION:Our Saturday afternoon Pexava salsa social\, in the heart of bustling Upper Street Angel\, central London! \nAmazing venue: A bright\, atmospheric and airy hall with wooden floor. Social dancing with great music and the chance to catch up and connect with salsa friends over snacks. \nBring your own drinks (no alcohol) \nAddress: 277A Upper Street\, Islington\, London\, N1 2TZ (next to the Islington fire station)\n5 mins walk from: Highbury & Islington or Angel Station \nEntry £10\nPay by cash or card at the door
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/pexava-matinee-social-saturday-2/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:New Unity\, 277A Upper St\, London\, N1 2TZ\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
