SUMMARY:ECI SATURDAY MAMBO SALSA BACHATA & MORE
DESCRIPTION:NO COVER CHARGE! \nECI SATURDAY MAMBO SALSA BACHATA & MORE\nat HOLLYWOOD CASINO JOLIET \nHollywood Casino Joliet\n1401 Gateway Blvd.\nJoliet\, IL 60431 \n4:00pm – 7:00pm\n– 4:00pm – 5:00pm: Dance Lesson\n– 5:00pm – 7:00pm: Open Dancing \nEvent Curator:\n– El Caobo Internacional (www.elcaobo.net) \nMusic by:\n– El Caobo \nDance Lesson by:\n– To Be Determined \nABOUT THE EVENT: \nGet ready for a night of nonstop dancing\, beautiful music\, and good vibes in the brand-new casino! Whether you’re a seasoned dancer or just looking to try something new\, this is the place to be.\n🕺💃 Salsa\, Bachata & More Select Saturdays\, 4PM – 7PM\n🎲 Casino energy + dance floor fire\n🍹 Drinks flowing\, smiles glowing\n💸 NO COVER CHARGE — just bring your best moves!\nInvite your friends\, dress to impress\, and let’s make this an unforgettable night together. The dance floor is waiting for YOU! 🔥 \nABOUT THE VENUE: \nHollywood Casino Joliet\, the new casino\, opened August 11\, 2025!\nIt is easy to get to—and impossible to forget.\nLocated off I-80 for a quick and easy getaway to gaming\, dining and entertainment! \nHollywood Casino Joliet has landed in their new\, modern location\, and they have leveled up the thrill with:\n* 1000+ Slots: Spin it. Win it. Love it.\n* Over 40 Live Table Games: High energy. High stakes. All the action.\n* ESPN BET Sportsbook: Game day hits different here. Cold drinks\, hot bets\, and wall-to-wall screens.\n* World-Class Dining: Big flavors. Bold names. Think Giada De Laurentiis and Shawn McClain.\n* Event Center: From epic parties to polished meetings\, they have the space to make it unforgettable. \nA whole new Hollywood is calling. You in? \n*******************************************\n#ElCaoboInternacional | #ElCaobo | #Salsa | #Mambo | #Bachata | #Merengue | #Chicago | #ECI | #SalsaChicago | #ChicagoSalsa | #BachataChicago | #chicagobachata | #MamboChicago | #ChicagoMambo | #NotJustDancingPARTYING | #MixMasters | #MamboClásicoConElCaobo | #Fania | #FaniaRecords | #RadioMamboClásico | #MamboClásico | #SalsaClásica | #pier31restaurant | #HollywoodCasinoJoliet | #SalsaTuesday | #TuesdaySalsa | #DancingIsAlwaysCoolerNearTheLake \n 
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/eci-saturday-mambo-salsa-bachata-more-at-hollywood-casino-joliet-joliet-il/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:Hollywood Casino Joliet\, 1401 Gateway Blvd\, Joliet\, IL\, 60431\, United States
CATEGORIES:Chicago
END:VEVENT
