SUMMARY:Salsa Bachata at the District
DESCRIPTION:SALSA & BACHATA AT THE DISTRICT – LOVE THEMED EDITION 🔥❤️\nGet ready\, Clearwater — the 500 block of Downtown Clearwater is about to turn into the hottest dance floor in the city!\nSalsa & Bachata Street Party that brings the music\, the movement\, and the passion straight to the streets.\nFrom 6 PM to 1 AM\, dance under the lights to nonstop Latin rhythms. Whether you’re dancing with your partner\, your crew\, or someone new\, the vibes will be undeniable.\nNew to dancing or want to sharpen your moves? Dance lessons by Weepa House will get everyone moving with confidence — no experience needed\, just bring the love and the energy.\nAnd when the street party hits its peak… we’re not done.\n🔥 The celebration continues with the official AFTER PARTY at Nash Keys\, happening right after — taking the energy indoors and turning it all the way up.\n✨ All happening on the 500 block of Downtown Clearwater\n🎶 Salsa • Bachata • Dance Lessons • Street Party • After Party\nHigh energy • One unforgettable night\nCome for the street party. Stay for the after party.\nClear your schedule — this is the one everyone will be talking about
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-at-the-district-afterparty/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:The District in Downtown Clearwater\, 528 Cleveland Street\, Clearwater\, FL\, 33755\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tampa
END:VEVENT
