SUMMARY:Bachata Pop-Up Party
DESCRIPTION:💃🔥🌟 𝐅𝐈𝐑𝐒𝐓 𝐄𝐕𝐄𝐑 𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐓𝐀 𝐏𝐎𝐏-𝐔𝐏 𝐏𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐘— 𝐒𝐀𝐓𝐔𝐑𝐃𝐀𝐘 𝐍𝐈𝐆𝐇𝐓🌟🔥💃\nBecause so many of you requested a Saturday social\, we’re making it happen! 🙌\nJoin us for our very first Bachata Pop-Up Party— a special one-night event with more weekend energy\, more dancing\, and more bachata vibes. ❤️‍🔥🎶\nBe there for the FIRST edition and help us kick this off in a big way! 🎉✨\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🎶 EVENT FLOW 🎶\n🕗 8:00–8:30 PM — Bachata Class (Open Level)\n👣 Beginner friendly + all levels welcome\n🤝 No partner needed\n🕣 8:30–11:00 PM — Bachata Social Dancing\n🎶 Your favorite bachata tracks\n💃 Fun\, friendly dance crowd\n🔥 Saturday night party feel\n📍 Location: The New Local Restaurante y Bar\n🍽️ Food & drinks specials\nEnjoy the special Saturday edition everyone’s been waiting for!\n🌟 First pop-up party ever\n💌 Bring friends\, dates\, or come solo\n💞 Meet new people\n💃 Dance more bachata\n🔥 Let’s pack the floor and make this first Saturday pop-up unforgettable! 🔥🎶✨
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/bachata-pop-up-party/
LOCATION:The New Local Restaurante\, 10432 SE Kent-Kangley Rd\, Kent\, WA\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/LDX-Latin-Dance-3-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
